headline: Does the Rally in Interactive Brokers Signal a Shift After Record 2025 Earnings?

The stock has attracted attention lately thanks to a series of impressive runs: up 4.2% over the past week, almost flat over the last month, but with a massive 39.6% gain year-to-date.
